Program: Outlook
Title: 30/11/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00lrkbx
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 1 Dec 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the British landmine clearer who was kidnapped by Khmer Rouge guerrillas in Cambodia. Also, a group of Guyanese transvestites challenging a law banning cross-dressing. And the son of musical legend Frank Zappa on keeping his father's music alive. Show less